2Pac is a rapper born on June 16, 1971 in Brooklyn, NY. 
Signed by Interscope Records in 1990, he started out with the group Digital Underground as a roadie. 
Signed to Death Row Records in 1996. 
Died September 13, 1996 in Las Vegas, NV, six days after being shot. 
Besides being a rapper, he also pursued a carreer in acting, starring in movies such as Juice and Above The Rim.
